ld to pursue their differences and to resolve their differences in that w=
ay. Our interest is in making sure those differences are resolved peacefu=
lly in a way that doesnt disrupt the free flow of commerce in the region.=




 This is a region of the world where billions of dollars of commerce is s=
hipped every day, and we certainly are interested in preventing any sort =
of disruptions that flow of commerce and goods.



