 that would have produced a better result.&nbsp; It's certainly appropriate=
 for historians to examine what are the longer-term consequences of that de=
cision.&nbsp; All of that is an entirely fair discussion for historians and=
 for the American people to consider.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoFooter" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoFooter" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">But that's not what Presi=
